{"tid":1897632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南韓極速傳播】 專家：新聞自由，反映真實疫情","createTime":"2020-02-25T22:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T23:40:38.000Z","uid":202464,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"04943142c4cfb7f9cf159177e997d1c6b1e9cc0a","tid":1897632,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:49:10.000Z","msg":"美國《時代》周刊有專家認為，南韓確診數字在短期內急升，與南韓有新聞自由及民主制度有關，目前南韓數字較能反映武漢肺炎的真實傳播能力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南韓喬治梅森大學（George Mason University Korea）的訪問學者阿布拉哈米安（Andray Abrahamian）指，確診數字在短期內急升，亦與南韓高度開放及透明有關，因當地檢測效率高，令消息流通，是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">該區少數有這些條件的國家</span></span>。"},{"pid":"2f3b43b9826a0361ea1baf53c9b2d367dc4c208d","tid":1897632,"uid":177213,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:51:10.000Z","msg":"我諗南韓係全亞洲唯一一個報感染實數嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fb70aeb50d16aaa3428aa4292e018671092da8","tid":1897632,"uid":169310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:53:38.000Z","msg":"韓國政府係有心抗疫，睇佢地醫療制度同應對體制就知，可借，班人民仲係亂發劍，唔洗手，政府做到再好再透明都冇用"},{"pid":"21888daeadc20643ab60bb420c9107d7e238c668","tid":1897632,"uid":36049,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89fb70aeb50d16aaa3428aa4292e018671092da8","tid":1897632,"uid":169310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:53:38.000Z","msg":"韓國政府係有心抗疫，睇佢地醫療制度同應對體制就知，可借，班人民仲係亂發劍，唔洗手，政府做到再好再透明都冇用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:57:33.000Z","msg":"d 韓國老粗衛氐意識係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193c6cd4eb4958208f783362bf3d8068786f9825","tid":1897632,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"2f3b43b9826a0361ea1baf53c9b2d367dc4c208d","tid":1897632,"uid":177213,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"reply